    AnswerBody:
      '"By Sarah Ferris, Melanie Zanona and Heather Caygle. The Senate late Wednesday unanimously approved a $2 trillion emergency package intended to stave off total economic collapse in the wake of the coronavirus crisis, bringing an end to more than five days of negotiations between senators and the Trump administration."',
